---
const stripImages = [
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509631179647-0177331693ae?w=300&q=80',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?w=300&q=80',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515886657613-9f3515b0c78f?w=300&q=80',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1496747611176-843222e1e57c?w=300&q=80',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1529139574466-a303027c1d8b?w=300&q=80',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502823403499-6ccfcf4fb453?w=300&q=80',
  'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517841905240-472988babdf9?w=300&q=80',
];
---

<section class="bg-dark py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex gap-2 mb-8 overflow-x-auto pb-2">
      {stripImages.map((img) => (
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-32 md:w-48 h-24 md:h-32 overflow-hidden">
          <img src={img} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all" />
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-8">
      <p class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-cream leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Inspiramos, comprometemos y desafiamos la excelencia creativa en la cultura visual contemporánea y más allá.
      </p>
      
      <div class="hidden md:flex gap-3 flex-shrink-0">
        <button class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-cream/50 flex items-center justify-center text-cream hover:bg-cream hover:text-dark transition-all">
          ←
        </button>
        <button class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-cream/50 flex items-center justify-center text-cream hover:bg-cream hover:text-dark transition-all">
          →
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
